---
title: Community
description: Solidus is an open source ecommerce solution built with Ruby on Rails and maintained by a community of passionate developers.
---

<div class="community-hero content-block content-block-xl position-relative text-center">
  <div class="container container-md">
    <h1 class="title">You’re going to <%= inline_svg("icons/heart-big.svg", class: "isvg animate-heart")%> this.</h1>
    <p class="lead mb-md-6 mb-3">Solidus is an open source ecommerce solution built with Ruby on Rails and maintained by a community of passionate developers.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="community-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="d-lg-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="community-data">
          <h3 class="title">23180+</h3>
          <p>
            Core commits since 2015
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="community-data">
          <h3 class="title"><%= data.project_stats.slack_members %>+</h3>
