          using it for your business, this is your chance to participate and
          contribute actively. Help Solidus keep growing!
        </p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://opencollective.com/solidus" target="_blank">Donate</a>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md mt-5 mb-5">
